        <div class="IndentMedium">
            <h3>To Convert One Suggestion at a Time</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>In the <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1">Snippet</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2">Variable</MadCap:conditionalText> Suggestions window pane, select the row that you want to convert to a <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1">snippet</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2">variable</MadCap:conditionalText>. </li>
                <li>
                    <MadCap:snippetText src="../../../General/Double-Click-Right-Click-Open.flsnp" /> The file opens with the suggested content highlighted.</li>
                <li>
                    <p>In Flare, insert the <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1">snippet</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2">variable</MadCap:conditionalText> (e.g., select <span class="Emphasis">Insert &gt; </span><span MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1" class="Emphasis">Snippet</span><span MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2" class="Emphasis">Variable</span>). </p>
                    <p MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">See  <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1"><MadCap:xref href="../../../../../../Flare/Snippets/Main-Activities/Inserting-Snippets.htm">Inserting Snippets</MadCap:xref></MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2"><MadCap:xref href="../../../../../../Flare/Variables/Main-Activities/Inserting-Variables.htm">Inserting Variables</MadCap:xref></MadCap:conditionalText> for more information about inserting <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1">snippets</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2">variables</MadCap:conditionalText>.</p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>